Version on Scratch: https://scratch.mit.edu/projects/636406901/

⭐️Controls⭐️

 W = up - S = down - A = to the Left - D = to the Right

 ⭐️Instruction⭐️

 Eat the fish, but not the junk in the water!  The blue fish are worth 5 points.  If you have 5 fish, you have won.  BUT BEWARE OF THE SNAKE!
